ever, as a big transparency

00:02:59.060 --> 00:03:01.110
measure for them.

00:03:01.110 --> 00:03:04.730
So each of these
companies took big strides

00:03:04.730 --> 00:03:05.790
for the right reasons.

00:03:05.790 --> 00:03:11.390
