00:38:16.746 --> 00:38:18.620
People want opportunities,
but a lot of time,

00:38:18.620 --> 00:38:20.245
there's powers that
be that pretty much

00:38:20.245 --> 00:38:24.310
prevent them from building their
version of the Congolese dream,

00:38:24.310 --> 00:38:25.420
if you'd say.

00:38:25.420 --> 00:38:28.890
So basically, I just want you
to be aware that the Congolese--

00:38:28.890 --> 00:38:31.750
